data.description: Welcome to 21 Onsville Place! This is the perfect townhome for anyone looking for a modern and beautiful property to call home. The exterior of the home features modern style with a fenced in backyard and spacious deck - perfect for hosting or relaxation. Upon entering the home you'll find a half bath connected to a spacious laundry room. Moving down the entry hall, you will be greeted with a sizable living room with a cozy fireplace and dining area. These rooms also offer gorgeous new wood floors, creating a modern look. Off the dining area is your kitchen that features great storage and a window overlooking the backyard. Up the carpeted stairs you will find two spacious bedrooms complete with roomy closets and a full bath. The entire townhouse has both newly painted walls and new flooring throughout. Are you ready to move in? Schedule your showing today!
